%F A382379 G.f.: 4*(1 - 3*x + 2*x^2 + 2*x^3 + x^4)/((1 + x)*(1 - 3*x + x^2)*(1 - x - x^2)). - _Andrew Howroyd_, Nov 16 2025
%e A382379 The triangles begin:
%e A382379   n=0:      3,     4,     5;
