%e A382379   ...
%e A382379 This sequence gives the middle column
%o A382379 (PARI) a(n) = my(t=fibonacci(n+1)+fibonacci(n-1)); 2*t*(t-1); \\ _Andrew Howroyd_, Nov 16 2025
